# iOS native project — generated on the macOS CI runner (Codemagic) each build, NOT committed.
# This repo is developed on Windows, which cannot run `cap add ios` / CocoaPods / Xcode. The
# project is rebuilt reproducibly from capacitor.config.ts + scripts/ios-configure.sh in CI.
# (android/ IS committed because it can be generated on Windows; ios/ cannot.)
/ios

